Package model

Class User

java.lang.Object
model.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Patient, Physician
public abstract class User extends Object
The abstract User class represents a basic user in a system. It includes properties such as the user's name, email, password, and address.

  • Constructor Details

    • User

      public User(String CF, String email, String password, String name, String surname, String sex, LocalDate birthdate, String nationality, String street, int civic_number, int cap, String city, String phone_number)
      Creates a new User object with the specified properties.
      Parameters:
      CF - the user's Codice Fiscale (tax code)
      email - the user's email address
      password - the user's password
      name - the user's first name
      surname - the user's last name
      sex - the user's gender
      birthdate - the user's date of birth
      nationality - the user's nationality
      street - the user's street address
      civic_number - the user's civic number (address number)
      cap - the user's postal code
      city - the user's city
      phone_number - the user's phone number
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if any of the specified values are null, or if the CF, email, or phone_number values are invalid
